07:59.000 --> 08:10.000
We predict a considerable movement of middle-western grains either to the Gulf and to southerly markets or perhaps to the Alabama Mississippi Georgia area.

08:10.000 --> 08:17.000
This would be feed grains primer or food grains that people have farmers in Tennessee who are absolutely.

08:17.000 --> 08:25.000
