12:08.000 --> 12:21.000
I understand that this may be a place where atomic energy will be used to good advantage in the blasting and the moving of dirt it may be necessary as part of the contemplation.

12:21.000 --> 12:36.000
This project does lend itself to the peaceful application of nuclear energy particularly in the section known as the divide cut which is just south of the Tennessee River.

12:36.000 --> 13:05.000
In this area the depth of cut is approximately 150 feet and by use of nuclear explosives detonated below the surface with no fallout or other radiation problems this excavation could be constructed at a cost at least 10% less expensive than if conventional excavation methods were used.

13:05.000 --> 13:34.000
